HEADWORD: chucker-out
<hw>chucker-out</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a person whose duty is to throw
troublemakers out of a bar or public meeting; a bouncer{5}.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> bouncer.</syn>⟦br⟧
